statement.tex:
\text{Using properties of determinants, prove that} \\
\small{\left\vert\begin{array}{ccc}
  2y & y-z-x & 2y \\
  2x & 2x & z-x-y \\
  x-y-x & 2x & 2x
\end{array}\right\vert=(x+y+z)^3}

step.context:
\textbf{On properties of determinants} \\
\text{What property of determinant could we use to} \\
\text{convert} 
\left\vert\begin{array}{cc}
  1 & 1 \\
  2 & 1
\end{array}\right\vert \text{ to }
\left\vert\begin{array}{cc}
  1 & 1 \\
  1 & 0
\end{array}\right\vert ?
